1. Custom Rules: Define your own rules and policies for specific security requirements.\
2. Integration with Security Services: Integrate Cloud Sentry with other security services to create a holistic security solution.\
3. Continuous Monitoring: Set up automated monitoring and periodic scanning of your cloud environment.\
